---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Neural Diwan">
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto bg-surface p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6 text-accent">About Neural Diwan</h1>
    <img src="/your-profile-image.jpg" alt="Neural Diwan" class="w-64 h-64 rounded-full mx-auto mb-6 object-cover" />
    <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">
      Neural Diwan is a platform dedicated to exploring the intersections of web development, data science, and machine learning.
    </p>
    <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">
      This blog showcases projects, insights, and tutorials that span these exciting domains, with a particular focus on their practical applications.
    </p>
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-text-primary">About This Project</h2>
    <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">
      Neural Diwan itself is built with modern web technologies, demonstrating the power of contemporary web development practices:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4 text-text-secondary">
      <li>Astro for blazing-fast static site generation</li>
      <li>GitHub Actions for continuous integration and deployment</li>
      <li>Google Cloud Platform (GCP) for hosting and infrastructure</li>
      <li>Google Kubernetes Engine (GKE) for containerized deployment</li>
    </ul>
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-text-primary">Connect With Us</h2>
    <div class="flex space-x-4">
      <a href="https://x.com/NeuralDiwan" class="text-link hover:text-accent">Twitter</a>
      <a href="https://github.com/DYAKOOO" class="text-link hover:text-accent">GitHub</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>